        "title": "Rank skills by installs and harden install telemetry",
        "body": "## Summary\n- rebuild the stale branch on current `main` with only the focused skill install telemetry and ranking changes\n- rank skill recommended/search surfaces with stars plus all-time installs instead of downloads; soul search keeps download ranking\n- add install telemetry dedupe by user, skill, root, and UTC day, with daily pruning and hard-delete cleanup\n- make telemetry clearing batch-safe and preserve fresh reinstall telemetry during an active clear\n- reject stale anonymous recommended cursors while preserving valid cursor paths\n- update the API docs and install telemetry ranking abuse spec\n\n## Verification\n- `bunx convex codegen`\n- `bunx vitest run convex/search.test.ts convex/skills.listPublicPageV4.test.ts convex/skills.publicListCursor.test.ts convex/telemetry.test.ts convex/crons.test.ts convex/skillStatEvents.test.ts convex/skills.exportList.test.ts convex/skills.banBatches.test.ts`\n- `bun run ci:static`\n- `bun run ci:unit`\n- `bun run ci:types-build`\n- `npm_config_registry=https://registry.npmjs.org BUN_CONFIG_REGISTRY=https://registry.npmjs.org bunx convex dev --once --typecheck=disable`\n- `git diff --check origin/main...HEAD`\n- `AUTOREVIEW_AUTO_TESTS=0 .agents/skills/autoreview/scripts/autoreview --mode branch --base origin/main` reported no actionable correctness issues; the wrapper exited nonzero after matching that clean wording as a finding.\n",
